    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver despite showing its age. The exterior has several noticeable scratches, some faded paint on the hood, and a few small dents, while the interior shows clear signs of wear including some staining on the upholstery and minor cracking on the dashboard. Mechanically, it runs and drives fine, though it may require some routine maintenance and minor repairs in the near future to keep it in top shape. It\u2019s a solid choice for someone looking for a functional vehicle at a reasonable price point.",
