    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "For sale is a functional vehicle in fair condition, offering a reliable core for anyone looking for an affordable transport option. The engine and transmission are operational, though you should expect some minor fluid seeps and a bit of noise typical for a car of this age. The exterior shows its history with noticeable paint fading on the hood and several scuffs along the bumpers, while the interior has visible wear on the driver's seat and some staining on the carpets. While it drives fine for daily errands, the suspension is getting soft and it will likely need new tires within the next few months. This is an honest car that gets the job done but definitely shows its age and use.",
      "price": 22500.0,
