      "description": "Hey there! Are you ready to fall in love? I\u2019m parting with this absolute stunner, and let me tell you, she is in pristine, showroom-level shape! It\u2019s been pampered since day one and honestly looks like it just rolled off the lot. If you've been looking for a total gem that drives like a dream, this is the one. I\u2019m so excited for someone to get behind the wheel and enjoy it as much as I have\u2014feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 43500.0,
