      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, preserved to a standard that exceeds even original showroom expectations. The exterior features a deep, mirror-like finish protected by a professional ceramic coating, with absolutely zero dings, chips, or road rash. Inside, the cabin remains in factory-fresh condition; the premium leather retains its original scent and suppleness, completely free from bolster wear or creasing. Every button, switch, and electronic feature operates with tactile precision. Mechanically, the car is flawless, backed by a comprehensive chronological binder of every service record since new. Always garage-kept under a breathable cover and never driven in inclement weather, this car represents a rare opportunity for a discerning collector or enthusiast who refuses to compromise. Includes all original keys, manuals, and a clean title in hand.",
